            "question_faqs_1": "Is this storage rack easy to install?",
            "answer_faqs_1": "Yes, our storage rack is very easy to install, taking only 10 to 15 minutes.  We provide clear installation instructions and a video guide, along with all necessary tools—no need to purchase additional items.  Should you have any questions, feel free to contact our professional service team anytime.",
