            "answer_faqs_2": "Free shipping on all items.",
            "question_faqs_3": "How long will it take for my order to arrive?",
            "answer_faqs_3": "From the time you place your order, it typically takes a total of 3-8 business days to be delivered.  This includes both order processing and shipping time.",
            "question_faqs_4": "What is the weight capacity of these shelves?",
            "answer_faqs_4": "The maximum load capacity for each shelf is clearly stated on its product page. Our products undergo rigorous quality testing. Please choose a model suitable for the weight of the items you plan to store and do not exceed the maximum limit to ensure safety.",
